BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kqlXzlGpAhdI30dtBYCFx
SUMMARY:New Member Party & Social
DTSTAMP:20260630T135112Z
DTSTART:20260708T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:[social]\nYou’ve joined the coolest crew in Houston—and now it’
	s time to celebrate! You’re officially part of a vibrant community of outd
	oor-loving\, fun-seeking\, down-for-anything adventurers. Whether you're b
